com.tencent.soter.core.model

类 SoterPubKeyModel

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.tencent.soter.core.model.SoterPubKeyModel

  • public class SoterPubKeyModel
extends java.lang.Object
    The public key model for App Secure Key and Auth Key. It consists the whole JSON that wrapper in the TEE, and the signature of the JSON generated in TEE. Developers should upload the JSON and signature to server
